OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,FITV News' Anna Youssef spoke to Sam's
OL,7,Ffamily about their worries over the
OL,8,Flevel crossing.
OL,10,FThe family of a marathon runner who
OL,11,Fwas struck by a train while listening
OL,12,Fto music has warned a "child will be
OL,13,Fnext" if action is not taken to make
OL,14,Fthe level crossing where he was killed
OL,15,Fsafer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
