OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,FSam Dudley, 29, was training for the
OL,7,FChester Ultra, and listening to music
OL,8,Fthrough his headphones, when he was
OL,9,Fhit by a train at Hoggs Hill Level
OL,10,FCrossing in Formby, Merseyside on 25
OL,11,FAugust 2025.
OL,13,FAn inquest later heard that while the
OL,14,Fwarning lights were red and the klaxon
OL,15,Fwas sounding, the "distraction" of his
OL,16,Fnoise cancelling earphones meant Sam
OL,17,Flikely never heard the danger coming.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
