FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,F"It was a tragic accident", Sam's
OL,7,Fmother Sandra said. "I've seen the
OL,8,Ffootage, he's happy, he's running and
OL,9,Fhe's just basically in his own little
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,F"He was doing his regular route and
OL,13,Fenjoying his run. He was distracted.
OL,14,FHe didn't come back from his run that
OL,15,Fday."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
