PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,FA Prevention of Future Deaths report
OL,7,Ffound that the crossing was "safe and
OL,8,Fcompliant," but the investigation
OL,9,Ffound there was "limited signage" and
OL,10,Frecommended more visual cues to alert
OL,11,Fpeople wearing headphones.
OL,13,FThe report stated: "Increasingly, more
OL,14,Fpeople wear earphones and are
OL,15,Ftherefore less aware of their
OL,16,Fsurroundings. Introducing clear
OL,17,Fpictorial signage on the gate, before
OL,18,Findividuals enter the 'decision point'
OL,19,Farea, such as an image of earphones
OL,20,Fwith a line through them, may help
OL,21,Falert users at the right moment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
