PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,FSandra insists the current setup is
OL,7,Fnot safe for the increasing footfall
OL,8,Fin the area.
OL,10,F"Originally it was not as accessible",
OL,11,Fshe said. "The public footpath which
OL,12,Fruns across the railway tracks has
OL,13,Fbeen improved so that's encouraging
OL,14,Fpeople to walk or cycle to the beach -
OL,15,Fand it is a main route to a school."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
