FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,FSandra is in the process of launching
OL,7,Fa petition to make the crossing safer,
OL,8,Fproposing a lockable pedestrian gate
OL,9,Fwhich turns from green to red when a
OL,10,Ftrain is approaching; an extra 'Think'
OL,11,Fgate closer to the tracks; and for the
OL,12,Fklaxon to be louder.
OL,14,FSam's brother Dan believes an
OL,15,Fadditional barrier is needed at the
OL,16,Fpoint of crossing because it is "only
OL,17,Fa matter of time" until someone else
OL,18,Fis killed.
OL,20,F"If they don't take action, it will be
OL,21,Fa child next", he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
