PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,FNetwork Rail has expressed its
OL,7,F"sincere thoughts" to the Dudley
OL,8,Ffamily and says they are in regular
OL,9,Fcontact with Sandra. However, they
OL,10,Fremain cautious about adding more
OL,11,Fphysical infrastructure.
OL,13,FSimon Butterworth, Network Rail North
OL,14,FWest route head of safety, said: "We
OL,15,Fnever want to see anyone lose their
OL,16,Flife on the railway and our thoughts
OL,17,Fremain with Sam Dudley's friends and
OL,18,Ffamily after his tragic death at Hoggs
OL,19,FHill level crossing in Formby last
OL,20,Fsummer.
OL,26,@vD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
