OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,F"After such tragedies, we are subject
OL,7,Fto multiple internal and external
OL,8,Finvestigations which are rightly there
OL,9,Fto learn everything possible to
OL,10,Fprevent such a terrible accident from
OL,11,Fhappening again. At the recent
OL,12,Finquest, the Coroner heard detailed
OL,13,Fevidence from a range of sources,
OL,14,Fincluding independent investigations,
OL,15,Fwhich confirmed that the crossing was
OL,16,Fsafe, compliant and operating as
OL,17,Fdesigned at the time of the incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,F"Since the inquest earlier this year
OL,7,Finto Mr Dudley's death, calls have
OL,8,Fbeen made about the introduction of
OL,9,Ffurther measures like lockable gates,
OL,10,Flouder sirens or more signage at Hoggs
OL,11,FHill. Unfortunately, while some may
OL,12,Fseem like safer solutions, they can in
OL,13,Ffact introduce further adverse risk.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778674272
OL,3,C'A child will be next': Family demands
OL,4,Csafer crossing after runner's death
OL,6,F"We continue to be in regular contact
OL,7,Fwith Sam's mother and are very open to
OL,8,Fworking with her as part of our
OL,9,Fcontinual commitment to get the
OL,10,Fmessage out to everyone to always
OL,11,Fstop, listen, and look both ways
OL,12,Fbefore ever attempting to cross live
OL,13,Frailway lines."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Sefton Council
OL,16,Fconfirmed that while the footpath is
OL,17,Fpublic, the crossing itself belongs to
OL,18,FNetwork Rail.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
